There is no problem with these people.

293
00:12:22,040 --> 00:12:23,840
They are all citizens of Daqian.

294
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:26,040
You shouldn't have just brought the soldiers.

295
00:12:26,040 --> 00:12:28,040
You should also bring doctors here.

296
00:12:29,200 --> 00:12:29,760
Yes.

297
00:12:29,760 --> 00:12:30,400
Prime Minister Lin.

298
00:12:30,400 --> 00:12:31,680
I'll do it right away.

299
00:12:40,920 --> 00:12:41,960
Coming.

300
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:46,120
You look like someone from a wealthy family.

301
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:47,450
Pick whatever you like.

302
00:12:47,680 --> 00:12:48,540
Take your time.

303
00:12:57,880 --> 00:12:59,120
You can't go in.

304
00:12:59,120 --> 00:12:59,840
If it were a few years ago,

305
00:12:59,840 --> 00:13:01,970
I would've killed you with one strike.

306
00:13:02,160 --> 00:13:03,040
You should be glad

307
00:13:03,040 --> 00:13:05,160
that Daqian respects the law.

308
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:08,160
Peasant.

309
00:13:18,280 --> 00:13:19,000
Send a message.

310
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,080
The secret passage has been discovered.

311
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,610
Tell everyone to evacuate.

312
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:25,160
Who are we sending the message to, boss?

313
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,600
To my wife at home.

314
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:27,720
Send it to Beijing.

315
00:13:28,160 --> 00:13:28,720
Sister,

316
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:29,580
take them down.

317
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:31,920
Go.

318
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:54,720
A perfect match,

319
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:56,120
and a prosperous family.

320
00:13:56,720 --> 00:13:57,760
May you have a harmonious union,

321
00:13:57,760 --> 00:13:59,290
and be of one heart forever.

322
00:13:59,960 --> 00:14:01,040
An excellent match,

323
00:14:01,040 --> 00:14:02,480
in perfect harmony.

324
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:04,120
Mutual respect,

325
00:14:04,120 --> 00:14:05,480
and a blissful life.

326
00:14:06,160 --> 00:14:07,320
Flying together,

327
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:08,960
and may you soon have a child.

328
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:10,160
Marital harmony,

329
00:14:10,160 --> 00:14:11,620
and growing old together.

330
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:13,000
Supporting each other,

331
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,660
and staying together always.

332
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:20,400
Congratulations.

